# Recipe Sharing Platform - Spring Boot

## Description
A Spring Boot-based recipe sharing platform where users can add, update, list, and delete recipes.

## Technologies Used
- Java 11+
- Spring Boot 2.x
- JPA & Hibernate
- H2 Database (for in-memory storage)
- JUnit 5 for unit testing
- Mockito for mocking dependencies in tests

## Features
- Add a new recipe
- List all recipes
- Update an existing recipe
- Delete a recipe

## Setup Instructions

### Prerequisites
- Java 11+
- Maven
- IDE (e.g., IntelliJ IDEA or Eclipse)

### Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/recipe-sharing-platform.git
cd recipe-sharing-platform
